These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, drama, action, epic
1. the person watching drama movies is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching epic movies is between the person watching crime movies and the person watching drama movies##2
3. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | epic | drama | action |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, water-polo, snowboarding, soccer
1. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Sport   | water-polo | cycling | soccer | snowboarding |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, pepper, spinach, corn
1. the person eating corn is on the left or right of the person eating cabbage##3
2. the person eating cabbage is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating spinach is between the person eating corn and the person eating pepper##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Food   | cabbage | corn | spinach | pepper |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
4 different games are played: canasta, mah-jongg, poker, go
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
2. the person playing poker is in an even position##4
3. the person playing go is between the person playing canasta and the person playing poker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |       3       |   4    |
| Game   | mah-jongg | canasta | go | poker |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-5::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, helicopter, tram, ship
1. the person driving the jet-ski is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Transport   | ship | jet-ski | tram | helicopter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-6::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, fonseca, bongani, aristoff
1. the fonseca-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the fonseca-smoker is on the left or right of the aristoff-smoker##3
3. the bongani-smoker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |  3   |    4    |
| Cigar   | bongani | chaman | aristoff | fonseca |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-7::.
