.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, coffee, milk, 7up
1. the person drinking coffee is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |      2       |     3      |  4   |
