.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-10::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, october, november, january
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
2. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person who's birthday is in january##2
3. the person who's birthday is in july is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
| Birthday   | november | january | october | july |

