.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-11::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, cain, fonseca, prince
1. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
2. the cain-smoker is in an even position##4
3. the vegafina-smoker is between the fonseca-smoker and the prince-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |    4    |
| Cigar   | prince | vegafina | fonseca | cain |

