.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-12::.
City: liverpool, edinburgh, hannover, rome
1. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
2. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
3. the person traveling to edinburgh is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |  3  |    4    |
| City   | hannover | edinburgh | rome | liverpool |

