.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-14::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, baking, dancing, board-games
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
2. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Hobby   | dancing | board-games | reading | baking |

