.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, white, ivory, purple
1. the person who likes white is the person who likes white##1
2. the person who likes purple is on the left or right of the person who likes ivory##3
3. the person who likes ivory is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who likes light-blue is in an even position##4
5. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who likes white##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Color   | ivory | purple | white | light-blue |

