.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-20::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, april, october, november
1. the person who's birthday is in october is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |         2          |    3    |    4     |
| Birthday   | june | november | october | april |

 